d] Referral page §2: Stats summary card\n   440→**Status**: Done\n   441→**Changes**:\n   442→- Created `apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralStatsCard.tsx`:\n   443→  - Fetches stats on mount via `getReferralStats(accessToken)` with cancellation guard\n   444→  - Four stat boxes in a grid: Referred Players, Active (7d), Total Volume (SOL), Total Earned (SOL)\n   445→  - `formatSol()` helper: lamports string → SOL with compact display (1.2k, 1M) for large values, 4 decimal places for small\n   446→  - Loading state: skeleton placeholders per stat box (28px height, pulse animation)\n   447→  - Error handling: silently falls back to zeros on fetch failure\n   448→- Updated `ReferralPage.tsx`: imported `ReferralStatsCard`, replaced §2 placeholder comment\n   449→- Added CSS in `index.css`: `.ref-stats-card` styles (card, 4-column grid, JetBrains Mono values, responsive 2-column at 600px)\n   450→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18). Platform typecheck passed. Pre-existing backend typecheck error (HealthDeps) — not introduced by this change.\n   451→\n   452→## Iteration 24 — 2026-03-25T13:26:36Z — OK\n   453→- **Log**: iteration-024.log\n   454→\n   455→## Iteration 25 — 2026-03-25 — OK\n   456→\n   457→**Item**: [frontend] Referral page §3: Pending balance card with claim flow\n   458→**Status**: Done\n   459→**Changes**:\n   460→- Created `apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralClaimCard.tsx`:\n   461→  - Fetches stats on mount via `getReferralStats()` for pending balance + breakdown\n   462→  - Displays unified pending balance prominently (2rem, JetBrains Mono, bold)\n   463→  - Breakdown rows: \"From referrals: X SOL\" + \"From fee rebates: Y SOL\" using `totalEarnedLamports` and `totalRebateLamports`\n   464→  - Claim button: disabled below threshold (0.01 SOL), shows \"Claiming...\" during request, \"Processing...\" while polling\n   465→  - Polls `GET /referral/claim/:claimId` every 3s until terminal status\n   466→  - Success state: green ba