{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015iGSQQwp52LYtCqNvsJnNr","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully read all three files. Here's a summary of what I found:\n\n## Files Summary\n\n### 1. **referral.ts** (Complete routes implementation)\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/routes/referral.ts`\n\nThis file contains 482 lines of Hono route handlers for the referral system:\n\n**Endpoints implemented**:\n- `POST /code` — Set or replace the player's referral code (with CODE_REGEX validation: 3-16 chars, lowercase alphanumeric + hyphens)\n- `POST /apply` — Link the authenticated player to a referrer via code\n- `GET /code` — Retrieve player's current referral code\n- `GET /referrer` — Check if player has a referrer\n- `GET /stats` — Get referral summary stats (referred count, active count, volume, earned, rebate, pending)\n- `GET /earnings` — Paginated per-game earnings log (page & limit params)\n- `POST /claim` — Request async payout of pending earnings (snapshots pending balance, emits REFERRAL_CLAIM_REQUESTED event)\n- `GET /claim/:claimId` — Poll claim status (ownership check enforced)\n\n**Key logic**:\n- Self-referral prevention\n- Duplicate code prevention (handles race conditions)\n- Unique referee constraint (one referrer per player)\n- Referral base URL: `https://taunt.bet/r`\n- Uses `emitEvent` for async claim processing\n- All endpoints require JWT authentication\n\n---\n\n### 2. **index.ts** (Route registration)\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/index.ts`\n\n**Referral route setup** (lines 94-99):\n```typescript\n// Referral routes — authenticated GET + POST endpoints (require JWT on all methods)\napp.use(\n  \"/referral/*\",\n  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret, requireAllMethods: true }),\n);\napp.route(\"/referral\", createReferralRoutes({ db, sql, config }));\n```\n\nReferral routes receive three dependencies:\n- `db` — Db client (see below)\n- `sql` — Raw postgres connection (for transactions)\n- `config` — Config object (includes `referralMinClaimLamports`, `referralDefaultRateBps`)\n\n**Event handler registration** (lines 181-184):\n```typescript\nregisterHandler(\n  EventTypes.REFERRAL_CLAIM_REQUESTED,\n  createClaimHandler({ db, connection, serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair }),\n);\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. **db.ts** (Referral type interfaces & DB methods)\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/db.ts`\n\n**Referral types** (lines 127–178):\n\n```typescript\nexport interface ReferralCode {\n  id: number;\n  wallet: string;\n  code: string;\n  created_at: Date;\n  updated_at: Date;\n}\n\nexport interface ReferralLink {\n  id: number;\n  referrer_wallet: string;\n  referee_wallet: string;\n  created_at: Date;\n}\n\nexport interface ReferralEarning {\n  id: number;\n  referrer_wallet: string;\n  referee_wallet: string;\n  round_id: string;\n  game_type: string;\n  wager_lamports: number;\n  fee_lamports: number;\n  referrer_earned_lamports: number;\n  referrer_rate_bps: number;\n  referee_rebate_lamports: number;\n  referee_rebate_rate_bps: number;\n  created_at: Date;\n}\n\nexport interface ReferralStats {\n  referred_count: number;\n  active_count: number;\n  total_volume_lamports: string;\n  total_earned_lamports: string;\n  total_rebate_lamports: string;\n  pending_lamports: string;\n}\n\nexport interface ReferralClaim {\n  id: string;\n  wallet: string;\n  amount_lamports: string;\n  status: \"pending\" | \"processing\" | \"completed\" | \"failed\";\n  tx_signature: string | null;\n  error: string | null;\n  requested_at: Date;\n  processed_at: Date | null;\n}\n```\n\n**DB methods** (lines 314–408):\n\n**Codes**:\n- `insertReferralCode(wallet, code)` — Insert new code\n- `getReferralCodeByWallet(wallet)` — Get wallet's code\n- `getReferralCodeByCode(code)` — Look up code owner\n- `upsertReferralCode(wallet, code)` — INSERT … ON CONFLICT UPDATE\n\n**Links**:\n- `insertReferralLink(referrerWallet, refereeWallet)` — Create link\n- `getReferralLinkByReferee(refereeWallet)` — Get referrer for a player\n- `getReferralLinksByReferrer(referrerWallet)` — Get all referred players\n\n**Earnings & Stats**:\n- `insertReferralEarning(params)` — Record earning from a round\n- `getPendingBalance(wallet)` — Sum earned + rebate minus completed claims\n- `getReferralEarnings(wallet, page, limit)` — Paginated earnings for referrer\n- `getReferralStats(wallet)` — Summary: referred count, active count, volumes, earnings\n\n**Claims & Rates**:\n- `insertReferralClaim(wallet, amountLamports)` — Create claim (status='pending')\n- `getReferralClaim(claimId)` — Fetch claim by UUID\n- `updateClaimStatus(claimId, status, meta)` — Update status + tx_sig/error\n- `getReferrerRate(wallet, defaultRateBps)` — Check `referral_kol_rates` table, fallback to default\n\nAll database methods are implemented at lines 782–978 with postgres.js SQL templates, including normalization functions for numeric field conversions and JSONB parsing."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a3c6e0ecb15bb6c7f (use SendMessage with to: 'a3c6e0ecb15bb6c7f' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 51454\ntool_uses: 8\nduration_ms: 34486</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"aa0285d4-bc35-4024-8afc-77d99fd4e541","uuid":"8ee82a0d-0a4d-4c4b-b38a-300b97430f4b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T13:44:50.674Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the full contents of these files in sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/:\n1. routes/referral.ts - the referral routes implementation\n2. index.ts - how routes are registered (especially referral routes)\n3. db.ts - the referral-related type interfaces and method signatures (search for \"Referral\" or \"referral\")\n\nI need the complete code of referral.ts especially, plus the DB interfaces for referral types.","agentId":"a3c6e0ecb15bb6c7f","